tiation.\n  This includes the Whitney extension theorem and the higher order\ninterpolation theorems related to Ulam-Zahorski problem. Finally, we discuss\nthe results concerning smooth functions that are independent of the standard\naxioms ZFC of set theory. We close with a list of currently open problems\nrelated to this subject.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jun 2018 14:18:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-29"}
